iv><div class="t m1d2 x73 h2d y152d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m8bb xc h2d y1456 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As Peter was soundly sleeping the last night in the </div><div class="t m43f x11 h2d y1d73 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prison, what took place? What appeared in the prison? </div><div class="t m1118 x11 h2d ycd8 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did the angel do and say ? </div><div class="t m1d5 x73 h2d y133b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m116 xc h2d y74a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What further did he•say, and what followed? </div><div class="t m127 x73 h2d y1c32 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m3bc xc h2d y19d5 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As Peter mechanically followed the angel, what did </div><div class="t m4a6 x11 h2d y1d9c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he think? </div><div class="t mbbc x14 h2d y1c6c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to. Where did the angel conduct him ? What did the </div><div class="t m79f x11 h2d y1c6d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">angel do when he had conducted Peter clear of the </div><div class="t mf95 x11 h2d y1f3b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prison? </div><div class="t m520 x16 h2d y1ccb ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m97d x74 h2d y1ccb ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">t. When Peter came to himself, what did he say? </div><div class="t m419 x17 h2d y1192 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Give the exact words. </div><div class="t me4 x14 h2d y111a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m1556 xc h2d y1119 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Where did he then go? How can you tell that </div><div class="t mf48 x17 h2d y111d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he had a reason for going there? What was going on </div><div class="t m2db x17 h2d y19c2 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there? </div><div class="t me4 x14 h2d yd49 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m589 xc5 h2d y14fc ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who came to the door when Peter knocked? </div><div class="t m16d x5b hb ybc1 ff2 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IN COUNTRIES AROUND 